comment: LHH shows that Ariza (HOU) cleanly strips the ball from Hayward (UTA) prior to any incidental contact to the arm.
Hood (UTA) legally contests Harden's (HOU) jump shot attempt.
Booker (UTA) grabs Howard's (HOU) arm affecting his ability to retrieve the rebound.
L-SLA shows that Harden (HOU) and Harrell (HOU) both make contact with Withey's (UTA) arm and affect his dunk attempt.
Hood (UTA) commits a take foul on Harden (HOU).
Booker (UTA) reaches in and makes contact with Terry's (HOU) arm.
Ariza (HOU) grabs and holds Hayward (UTA), affecting his FOM as he attempts to get open during the inbounds play.
Beverley (HOU) grabs Burke's (UTA) jersey, affecting his RSBQ after he receives the hand-off pass.

Hood (UTA) draws Harden (HOU) into the air toward him to defend the shot. Harden does not maintain a vertical position and is moving toward Hood in the air, therefore the contact between the players is deemed a shooting foul on Harden.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that Hood (UTA) was attempting a 3 point field goal when he was fouled by Harden (HOU) was confirmed.
Johnson (UTA) makes contact with Terry's (HOU) arm and body that affects his ability to secure the ball.
